title: OSU police probing use of pepper spray in melee
description: A brawl broke out between Michigan and Ohio State players Saturday after the Wolverines planted their flag at midfield in the Horseshoe following their upset of the second-ranked Buckeyes.
author: Jake Trotter

title: Day: 4th straight loss to U-M 'not easy to accept'
description: No. 2 Ohio State fell 13-10 to rival Michigan on Saturday, likely ending the Buckeyes' hopes of returning to the Big Ten title game next week while also raising questions about coach Ryan Day's job security.
author: Jake Trotter

title: 'The impact of defeat is massive' - what to look out for in Liverpool v Man City
description: BBC Sport previews Sunday's massive Premier League title game between Liverpool and Manchester City at Anfield.

title: 'Title race on' - how Odegaard & Saka are keeping Arsenal hopes alive
description: As Arsenal move second with an emphatic win at West Ham, BBC Sport looks at how "deadly duo" Martin Odegaard and Bukayo Saka are keeping their title hopes alive.

title: Russell inherits Qatar pole as Verstappen demoted by grid penalty
description: George Russell will start Sunday's Qatar Grand Prix from pole position after Max Verstappen was given a one-place grid penalty for impeding the Brit during qualifying.

title: Britain's Pulling becomes F1 Academy champion
description: Britain's Abbi Pulling won the 2024 F1 Academy title in Qatar on Saturday.

title: College football live updates: Texas-Texas A&M rivalry renewed
description: It's fantastic that these two longtime rivals are finally playing each other again. And it's made even better by the stakes. Follow along with us.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: No. 5 Notre Dame clinches College Football Playoff spot with 2 pick-6s in 49-35 win over USC
description: USC twice drove toward a touchdown, only to see those plays go the other way on costly interceptions.
